    "For example, in studying partisanship, how does the policy topic of a Congressional bill relate to the ideology of its sponsor?",
    "We assume the researcher has specified a resource-intensive procedure for measuring the economic concept that we would be satisfied with if it could be scaled.",
    "Because it may be prohibitively costly or time-consuming, the researcher hopes to automate their existing measurement procedure and instead use an LLM to cheaply produce these labels.",
